headline: Texas Pacific: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DALLAS (AP) — Texas Pacific Land Corporation (TPL) on Wednesday reported profit of $116.1 million in its second quarter. On a per-share basis, the Dallas-based company said it had profit of $5.05. The landowner posted revenue of $187.5 million in the period.
